race.description: Race Revolution Annual Pest Management Battlers H
race.comment: DEEMED PSYCHO (2) has missed the frame at his last two but did run well three back when third (20.40) in a Grade 6 at this track. Can make amends this time. SLEEK ASSASSIN (5) jumped cleanly and went straight to the lead, holding on for a place when second (20.48) at this track in a Maiden over 366m. Expecting another good run. SOMERSET BLUEY (7) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (20.52) at this track. Key player if finds best. GRAPHITE (1) can sneak into the finish with the right run.
